"TCP/UDP port number (443 for HTTPS, 25 for SMTP, 853 for DNS-over-TLS, etc.)"
msgstr "TCP / UDP-portnummer (443 for HTTPS, 25 for SMTP, 853 for DNS- over- TLS, osv.)"

